The '''Well of Goodwill''' was a special well located east of [[Varrock]] [[Varrock West Bank|West Bank]]. Players could donate [[coins]] or [[items]] (which were counted for their value in gold coins), and for every million coins donated, [[Jagex]] donated one dollar to a charity listed on the well's interface.

It only accepted certain items, and coins in multiples of 1,000.
